## What I Fixed

1. **Map Marker Updates** 
   - When AI edits contain location keywords (restaurant, cafe, temple, etc.), the map will refresh
   - Calls `window.refreshMapMarkers()` if available

2. **History with localStorage**
   - All edits are now saved to browser localStorage
   - History persists even if you close the browser
   - Undo/redo buttons now work properly
   - No database needed!

